title: ValleyDevFest 2016 Announced
brief: Central California GDGs (Fresno, Visalia, Oakdale, Modesto) are proud to announce the fifth annual ValleyDevFest 2016 which is the biggest Google related event in the California Central Valley! The event will take place on the 22nd of October (Saturday) in Fresno.

title: Conference T-Shirt are available and Tickets are on Eventbrite
brief: Buy T-shirts until 26th of September counting as a ticket or you can choose to buy a ticket. The earlier the better.
